The focus of this book, Early Modern English Medical Texts (EMEMT), is an electronic
```
historical corpus of medical writing from the period 1500-1700. The corpus is the out-
come of team work. The compilers are Irma Taavitsainen, Paivi Pahta, Turo Hiltunen,
Ville Marttila, Martti Makinen, Maura Ratia, Carla Suhr, and Jukka Tyrkké.! EMEMT
contains a two-million word, structured sample of the register, representing the full
