9. Conclusion
The current chapter is intended to give users of EMEMT Presenter some advice about
how to begin processing the EMEMT corpus. It is important to remember that help,
both general and context-sensitive, is available within EMEMT Presenter. Further-
more, before starting work with the corpus in earnest, it is sensible to spend some
time acquainting oneself with the structure of the program and the manner in which
it presents the EMEMT corpus. By these means users can discover what options the
program has and how these can be customised to best suit their needs. The program
does not alter or disturb the structure of the EMEMT corpus in any way and the results
of any operation with EMEMT Presenter can be stored on disk and processed later with
other software if users so wish.
